data.description: Welcome to 14 Melody Drive! This beautiful 5 bedroom plus a loft, 3 bath home is spacious, move-ready, and nestled in the heart of Pooler, GA. It has great curb appeal, an attached 2-car garage, and an elongated driveway with ample parking. Sip your morning coffee on the lovely front porch or make wonderful summer memories on the back patio overlooking the large, fenced backyard. Inside, the floor plan is open, airy, and welcoming. The kitchen is stylish and functional with all stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and views of the family room. There is also a separate, formal dining room perfect for celebrations and hosting. All the bedrooms are generously sized with walk-in closets. There is a loft located upstairs that can be used as an office, media room, or even a play area. The possibilities are endless. This home has been well-maintained, so just bring your furniture and decorating ideas! Don't miss it! Schedule your home tour today.
